      "file": "c85.wav",
      "text": "When I dictate a long passage I want the engine to keep up without dropping words, handle the natural pauses where I stop to think, and still get the domain terms right, things like Kubernetes and Postgres and FluidAudio, even when I am talking quickly and running sentences together the way I actually do when I am heads down on a problem.",
