        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c87",
      "file": "c87.wav",
      "text": "The plan is straightforward even if it is tedious. I am going to land the early pull requests first, get reviews while the later steps are still being figured out, and give a rough sense of timelines without pretending the hard part is solved. I do not know exactly how long the last step will take, so I would rather say that out loud than guess and be wrong later.",
      "source": "human",
      "tags": [
        "long",
        "status"
      ],
      "condition": "noisy",
      "checks": {
        "stt": {
          "biasTerms": [],
